After adding or changing a scheduled item using [schedule.present](https://docs.saltstack.com/en/latest/ref/states/all/salt.states.schedule.html#salt.states.schedule.present) the schedule does not run until the minion is restarted. Running [schedule.reload](https://docs.saltstack.com/en/latest/ref/modules/all/salt.modules.schedule.html#salt.modules.schedule.reload) has no effect.
